setMode

public void setMode(java.lang.Object mode)
Sets the reset mode

Parameters:
mode - the reset mode specification. Must be one of the following values:
  • soft, for soft reset,
  • mixed, for mixed reset
  • hard, for hard reset
  • merge, for merge reset
  • keep, for keep reset
